<header class="article-header">
<h1 class="article-title">
The Reading Brain in the Digital Age: Why Paper Still Beats Screens
</h1>
<div class="article-dek">
E-readers and tablets are becoming more popular as such technologies improve, but reading on paper still has its advantages
</div>
<div class="article-author article-date">
By <a href="http://www.scientificamerican.com/author/ferris-jabr">Ferris Jabr</a>
</div>
<div class="article-socialVertical">
<div id="shareFloat">
<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/&amp;text=The Reading Brain in the Digital Age: Why Paper Still Beats Screens"><i class="icon-twitter icon-large"></i></a>
<a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?p[url]=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/"><i class="icon-facebook icon-large"></i></a>
<a target="_blank" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/"><i class="icon-googleplus icon-large"></i></a>
<a target="_blank" class="reddit" href="http://www.reddit.com/submit" onclick="window.open('http://www.reddit.com/submit?url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/&newwindow=1', 'external'); return false"><i class="icon-reddit"></i></a>
<a href="#" class="overlay-controller" id="emailForm" data-title="The Reading Brain in the Digital Age: Why Paper Still Beats Screens" data-url="http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/" data-summary="E-readers and tablets are becoming more popular as such technologies improve, but reading on paper still has its advantages"><i class="icon-envelope"></i></a>
<a href="http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/the-reading-brain-in-the-digital-age-why-paper-still-beats-screens/?print=true" rel="nofollow"><i class="icon-print"></i></a>
</div>
